{
  "name": "LeaderLines",
  "summary": "<p>该对象不是一个集合；没有表示单个引导线的对象。</p>\n<p>此对象只适用于饼图。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>LeaderLines</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>LeaderLines</strong>对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例图表一上的数据系列一添加数据标签和蓝色引导线。如果看不到引导线，则该示例代码将失败。在这种情况下，可从饼图中手动拖出其中一个数据标签以便显示引导线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartObjects2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    chartObjects2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasDataLabels</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    chartObjects2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataLabels</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Position</span> = xlLabelPositionBestFit\n    chartObjects2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasLeaderLines</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    chartObjects2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeaderLines</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 上的第三个数据系列的引导线粗细。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series3 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(series3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeaderLines</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表图表的引导线。引导线将数据标签连接到数据点。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<p>*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/  </p>\n<p>function test() {  </p>\n<p> let myObject = Application.ActiveWorkbook  </p>\n<p> if (myObject.Application.Value == &quot;ET&quot;) {  </p>\n<p> alert(&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;)  </p>\n<p> } else {  </p>\n<p> alert(&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;)  </p>\n<p> }  </p>\n<p>}</p>\n",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Border",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Border</strong>对象，它代表对象的边框。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 上的第二个数据系列的引导线粗细。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(series2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeaderLines</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作表上第一个图表的数据系列 3 添加线条样式为实线的引导线。如果看不到引导线，则本示例代码将失败。这种情况下，可以手动将数据标签之一拖出饼图以便让引导线显示。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Ser</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Ser</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasLeaderLines</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Ser</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeaderLines</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlContinuous\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Border",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Format",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong>ChartFormat</strong>对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将图表工作表 Chart1 上的第一个数据系列的引导线发光半径设置为5磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    series1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeaderLines</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Glow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Radius</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表���第一个图表的数据系列 1 的引导线的粗细设置为2磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    series1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeaderLines</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "ChartFormat",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
