      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例删除图表工作表 Chart1 上的第一个数据系列的引导线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    series1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeaderLines</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除第一张工作表上第一个图表的数据系列 1 的引导线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    series1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeaderLines</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
